workflowDefinition.description:
A developer makes changes in their sandbox for one or more packages. We may have one or more developers working on changes for different or the same packages. This means a many-to-many relationship between developer & packages.
If a package can be deployed to a second development environment and its tests run, then it is ready to be deployed to a test/QA/UAT environment. This test/QA/UAT environment is different from a developer sandbox in that it is a *configuration* environment and has much more data.
